        {
            "title": "德永佳盈利倒退但派特別息 股份午後復牌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德永佳(00321)派年度成績表，純利雖然倒退，但為慶祝成立50周年將派特別股息；該公司股份將於下午復牌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：德永佳官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250611_FI_source-web_00321.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：德永佳官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250611_FI_source-web_00321.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：德永佳官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司公布，截至今年3月底止年度歸屬公司普通權益所有者溢利1.16億元，按年倒退12.29%；每股盈利8.4仙，按年跌12.5%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">儘管純利倒退，但德永佳表示，在秉持為股東創造價值的承諾，擬派末期息每股1仙，另為慶祝公司成立50周年將派特別末期息每股5仙；連同已派中期息及特別中期息每股合供4仙，全年每股派10仙，較對上年度增加42.86%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在截至今年3月底止年度，德永佳總收入55.85億元，按年升4.1%。受越南工廠擴張及產品組合改變影響，毛利率降至23.6%，按年減少2.7個百分點，再加上受多項非經營因素包括因收購及擴建越南工廠產生融資成本2000萬元、碳排放費2200萬元、紅海危機導致運費增加1500萬元，以及被徵收廣州倉庫帶來的8900萬元收益，純利亦告倒退。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"公司官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/fi_texwinka_00321_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"公司官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/fi_texwinka_00321_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">公司官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">不過，公司繼續維持良好財務狀況，3月底時現金及現金等價物達16.33億元，未動用銀行信貸達60.2億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">展望未來，德永佳對紡織及零售市場保持審慎樂觀態度，其中零售及分銷業務，公司有信心在一系列戰略調整後，將逐步恢復盈利能力。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15004154-%e5%be%b7%e6%b0%b8%e4%bd%b3%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e5%80%92%e9%80%80%e4%bd%86%e6%b4%be%e7%89%b9%e5%88%a5%e6%81%af-%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%bd%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%be%a9%e7%89%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/00321-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-12 12:35:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "半日收市︱全程報跌 恒指半日回吐121點報24244點 創新藥股熱炒 中生製藥藍籌最強",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中美貿易框架細節尚待公布，市場回復審謹，港股今早全程回吐；創新藥股受捧，中國生物製藥(01177)成撐市主力。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中國生物製藥官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/01177-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中國生物製藥官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/01177-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中國生物製藥官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早低開143點後持續「潛水」，最低曾見24153點，跌213點，其後內地A股倒升，港股跌幅亦收窄，但高位也只見24288點，仍跌78點；恒指中午收報24244點，跌121點或0.5%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"中國生物製藥官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/01177-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"中國生物製藥官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/01177-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">中國生物製藥官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"中國生物製藥官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/01177-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"中國生物製藥官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/01177-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">中國生物製藥官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230724_FI_source-web_02359-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230724_FI_source-web_02359-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：藥明康德官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/紫金礦業官網.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/紫金礦業官網.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\"></h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"中國生物製藥官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/01177-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">中國生物製藥官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"中國生物製藥官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/01177-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">中國生物製藥官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230724_FI_source-web_02359-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：藥明康德官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/紫金礦業官網.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\"></h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數再度跑輸，半日挫57點或1.05%，報5393點；國企指數跌45點或0.51%，報8820點。主板半日成交1256.39億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日跌116點，報24227點，低水18點。科指期貨跌60點，報5394點，高水不足1點。國指期貨跌46點，報8811點，低水9點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中國生物製藥官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/01177-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中國生物製藥官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/01177-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中國生物製藥官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創新藥概念成為今早熱門炒作對象，恒生創新藥指數半日升3.94%，報2849點，身兼恒指與恒生創新藥指數成分股的中生製藥表現尤其突出，今早非但逆市裂口揚升，最高曾見5.62元，飆17.82%；中午收報5.49元，仍漲15.09%，半日成交19.32億元，單一股份已令恒指跌少近12點，也是今早對恒指提供最多點數進賬的藍籌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中生製藥資本市場負責人雷鳴，在近日出席於美國舉行的高盛全球醫療健康年會時透露，即將有一筆標誌性的重磅對外授權落地，又指創新產品收入佔比已由2018年的16%，升至去年的42%，料到了2027年可進一步升至60%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">多隻創新藥概念股亦借勢炒上，綠葉製藥(02186)漲6.59%，報3.72元；康哲藥業(00867)升5.32%，報11.88元，創52周新高；博安生物(06955)升5.35%，報14.98元；百濟神州(06160)也升5.41%，報167.5元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230724_FI_source-web_02359-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230724_FI_source-web_02359-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：藥明康德官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藍籌升幅榜首5位中，多達4隻是藥股，除了穩佔榜首的中生製藥外，藥明康德(02359)升4%，報77.95元，創52周新高；同系藥明生物(02269)漲3.57%，報27.6元；翰森製藥(03692)也升3.82%，報29.9元，升辷年高位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於藍籌升幅5大榜上唯一並非藥股的是紫金礦業(02899)，半日升5.72%，報20.15元，刷新歷史高位，是表現次佳恒指成分股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金價造好，是推動紫金逆市揚升的主要原因，其他金礦股亦普遍報升。招金礦業(01818)亦創新高，升5.19%，報21.3元；赤峰黃金(06693)升2.8%，報29.35元；山東黃金(01787)也升2.87%，報25.1元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/紫金礦業官網.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/紫金礦業官網.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">熱門股泡泡瑪特(09992)亦再度破頂，最多曾再升5.04%，衝上283.4元；中午收報273元，仍逆市升1.19%，報273元，半日成交46.42億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅科股則跌多升少，「ATMXJ」當中只有美團(03690)逆市微升0.28%，報144.2元；表現最差的是阿里巴巴(09988)，跌2.03%，報116元；小米(01810)也跌1.66%，報53.2元；京東(09618)則跌0.82%，報132.8元；騰訊(00700)跌0.58%，報515元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，宣布配股向市場「抽水」的地平線機器人，今早應聲受壓，但暫仍穩守配股價6.93元之上，今早跌至低位6.95元後便見初步支持，中午收報7.1元，跌幅收窄至4.57%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15004144-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%85%a8%e7%a8%8b%e5%a0%b1%e8%b7%8c-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%9b%9e%e5%90%90121%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b124244%e9%bb%9e-%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e8%97%a5",
